vatar/416480753e05e9fca9bc304151e8220b?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/416480753e05e9fca9bc304151e8220b?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/416480753e05e9fca9bc304151e8220b?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1575959508, "last_modified": 1575959508}, "last_reply_by": "ChefIsAwesome", "last_touched": 1681193133, "title": "公司今天将开始第三轮裁员，非常痛苦", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/931451", "created": 1681177970, "deleted": 0, "content": "疫情其间，公司业绩掉的很厉害，21 年裁过两次研发。22 年虽然上海经历封城，但整体业绩情况还能维持，没有继续裁员。今年开年第一季度，本来期望疫情结束后的业务大幅增长并没有到来，反而进一步急剧萎缩。老板找我讨论了一周，最终还是决定，之前剩下的 20 个研发，再裁掉 10 个。只保留最低维护人力。\r\n\r\n下午就会执行，感觉很痛苦。", "content_rendered": "<p>疫情其间，公司业绩掉的很厉害，21 年裁过两次研发。22 年虽然上海经历封城，但整体业绩情况还能维持，没有继续裁员。今年开年第一季度，本来期望疫情结束后的业务大幅增长并没有到来，反而进一步急剧萎缩。老板找我讨论了一周，最终还是决定，之前剩下的 20 个研发，再裁掉 10 个。只保留最低维护人力。</p>\n<p>下午就会执行，感觉很痛苦。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1681177970, "replies": 77, "id": 931451}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/02e7/4f10/27_large.png?m=1655527806", "name": "photograph", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/02e7/4f10/27_normal.png?m=1655527806", "title": "摄影", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/photograph", "topics": 457, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Photograph", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/02e7/4f10/27_mini.png?m=1655527806", "stars": 1017, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 27, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 367026, "username": "weishao666", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/weishao666", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/690f81902891f1bb72bbf56f0b551838?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/690f81902891f1bb72bbf56f0b551838?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/690f81902891f1bb72bbf56f0b551838?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1543592881, "last_modified": 1637735467}, "last_reply_by": "LXGMAX", "last