\n请教一下，用什么扩展坞合适（经济实惠型）", "content_rendered": "<p>14 英寸 MacBook Pro - 深空灰色</p>\n<p>硬件：\n96W USB-C 电源适配器\n配件套件\n带有触控 ID 的背光妙控键盘 - 中文 (拼音)\n96GB 统一内存\n三个雷雳 4 端口，以及 HDMI 端口、SDXC 卡插槽、耳机插孔和 MagSafe 3 端口\n2TB 固态硬盘\n14 英寸 Liquid 视网膜 XDR 显示屏²\nApple M2 Max (12 核中央处理器、38 核图形处理器和 16 核神经网络引擎)</p>\n<p>从上海发货。</p>\n<p>请教一下，用什么扩展坞合适（经济实惠型）</p>\n", "last_modified": 1681112277, "replies": 68, "id": 931269}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1680100332", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1680100332", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 12581, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1680100332", "stars": 6360, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 600134, "username": "szzys", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/szzys", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a695196ab82f3bbefaa9543ec18cb06e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a695196ab82f3bbefaa9543ec18cb06e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a695196ab82f3bbefaa9543ec18cb06e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1667423296, "last_modified": 1667423296}, "last_reply_by": "gamekiller0010", "last_touched": 1681135936, "title": "广东移动出海又绕路了，跑上海去了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/931324", "created": 1681121750, "deleted": 0, "content": "省网那群人不知道优化个什么。\r\n前段时间申请了条 PTN ，发现不如 PON 专线，于是找人提了工单上去做出海优化。\r\n2 天后醉了，优化没成功，全省的出海原来走广州出，现在变成走上海出去了。\r\n本来到香港就够慢了，现在原有基础徒增 60ms ，接近电信质量了。\r\n头大了。\r\n\r\n存心搞事情啊。", "content_rendered": "省网那群人不知道优化个什么。<br />前段时间申请了条 PTN ，发现不如 PON 专线，于是找人提了工单上去做出海优化。<br />2 天后醉了，优化没成功，全省的出海原来走广州出，现在变成走上海出去了。<br />本来到香港就够慢了，现在原有基础徒增 60ms ，接近电信质量了。<br />头大了。<br /><br />存心搞事情啊。", "last_modified": 1681121790, "replies": 64, "id": 931324}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 4198, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1100, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 398207, "username": "VoiceEXONE", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/VoiceEXONE", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9000/a5e7/398207_mini.png?m=1680064636", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9000/a5e7/398207_normal.png?m=1680064636", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9000/a5e7/398207_large.png?m=1680064636", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9000/a5e7/398207_xlarge.png?m=1680064636", "created": 1554275260, "last_modified": 1680064636}, "last_reply_by": "ihciah", "last_touched": 1681190727, "title": "如何看待跟拒绝朋友或亲属让你办信用卡，实施套现的行为", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/931310", "created": 1681119296, "deleted": 0, "content": "> 如题，已为其办了一张信用卡，目前还找我让办信用卡供其使用（套现操作）维系其小公司运作，目前说不清怎么办？", "content_rendered": "<blockquote>\n<p>如题，已为其办了一张信用卡，目前还找我让办信用卡供其使用（套现操作）维系其小公司运作，目前说不清怎么办？</p>\n</blockquote>\n", "last_modified": 1681119296, "replies": 61, "id": 931310}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 54967, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181", "stars": 8324, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 254353, "username": "FaiChou", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/FaiChou", "website": "https://faichou.com", "twitter": "FaiChou_zh", "psn": "", "github": "FaiChou", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_mini.png?m=1680507813", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_normal.png?m=1680507813", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_large.png?m=1680507813", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_xlarge.png?m=1680507813", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_xlarge.png?m=1680507813", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_xlarge.png?m=1680507813", "created": 1505371596, "last_modified": 1680507813}, "last_reply_by": "Bigglesworth", "last_touched": 1681191990, "title": "有多少小伙伴用了两天 Arc 又放弃了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/931274", "created": 1681113356, "deleted": 0, "content": "我是这样的, 开始感觉 Arc 好厉害, 各种功能好炫酷, 打开网页也是很快.\r\n\r\n但是用了一阵子, 真是习惯不了.\r\n\r\n最习惯不了的是没有书签的概念, 比如导入的 Chrome 书签, 点击一下结果在当前书签打开它了, 而在其他浏览器是开启一个 tab 来打开这个书签, 也就是说, 导入的 chrome 书签是一个个未激活的 tab.\r\n\r\n后来发现内存占用也很高, 毕竟是 chrome 内核嘛.\r\n\r\n问了一圈之前夸赞 Arc 的小伙伴, 基本都放弃了..\r\n\r\n说说你们喜欢或者不喜欢它的理由吧. 可能有些很赞的功能没发掘呢.", "content_rendered": "<p>我是这样的, 开始感觉 Arc 好厉害, 各种功能好炫酷, 打开网页也是很快.</p>\n<p>但是用了一阵子, 真是习惯不了.</p>\n<p>最习惯不了的是没有书签的概念, 比如导入的 Chrome 书签, 点击一下结果在当前书签打开它了, 而在其他浏览器是开启一个 tab 来打开这个书签, 也就是说, 导入的 chrome 书签是一个个未激活的 tab.</p>\n<p>后来发现内存占用也很高, 毕竟是 chrome 内核嘛.</p>\n<p>问了一圈之前夸赞 Arc 的小伙伴, 基本都放弃了..</p>\n<p>说说你们喜欢或者不喜欢它的理由吧. 可能有些很赞的功能没发掘呢.</p>\n", "last_modified": 1681113356, "replies": 56, "id": 931274}]